SUMMARY:Cynthia Lee Fontaine Presents: Drag Brunch at the Punch
DTSTAMP:20260620T130334Z
DTSTART:20260620T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Looking for the ultimate Houston drag brunch experience? Whethe
	r you're planning a bachelorette party\, a birthday celebration\, or just 
	want a daytime drag show without the late-night crowd\, this is your event
	. Drag Brunch at The Punch is a monthly extravaganza featuring fierce perf
	ormances\, sassy audience games\, and unforgettable live drag performances
	 ? paired with brunch cocktails\, mimosas\, and bites. The perfect daytime
	 LGBTQ event for anyone who loves fabulous entertainment before sundown. P
	roduced by RuPaul's Drag Race fan-favorite Cynthia Lee Fontaine\, each sho
	w features Houston drag queens bringing show-stopping numbers\, big laughs
	\, and serious talent. Perfect for girls' day out\, gay brunch\, Pride cel
	ebrations\, and anyone looking for a fun Saturday activity in Houston. No 
	late nights required ? just good drinks\, great queens\, and the best drag
	 brunch ticket in town. Grab your tickets now. Please note that Cynthia wi
	ll not be making an appearance.\nIMPORTANT TIMES: 10:30 AM BOX OFFICE OPEN
	S SEATING BEGINS AT 11:00AM - SHOWTIME IS AT 12:00PM This show is 18 & ove
	r with valid\, government-issued photo ID. Cameras and video/audio recordi
	ng devices are not permitted. $.25 per each ticket sold for a majority of 
	events at Punch Line benefits Comedy Gives Back\, a safety net for the com
	edy community. For more information\, please visit www.comedygivesback.com
	 Our events often run for multiple dates/times. Before purchasing\, please
	 ensure that you can attend the specific event\, date\, and time that is l
	isted on the event page. There are no refunds/exchanges unless an event is
	 cancelled/postponed.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/cynthia-lee-fontaine
	-presents-drag-brunch-houston-texas-06-20-2026/event/3A006435FE323D1A\n\nF
	rom Punch Line Comedy Club
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/cynthia-lee-fontaine-presents-drag-brunch-
	houston-texas-06-20-2026/event/3A006435FE323D1A
GEO:29.7534;-95.364
LOCATION:Punch Line Houston\, 1204 Caroline Street\, Houston\, TX
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:punch-line-comedy-club
CATEGORIES:Punch Line Comedy Club
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
